---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const paymentPolicy = [
  {
    title: "1. Introduction",
    content:
      "This Payment Policy outlines the terms regarding deposits, withdrawals, and transaction processing on VertexOption. By using our services, you agree to comply with this policy.",
  },
  {
    title: "2. Accepted Payment Methods",
    content:
      "VertexOption supports various payment methods, including bank transfers, credit/debit cards, and e-wallets. The available options may vary depending on your location.",
  },
  {
    title: "3. Deposit Process",
    content:
      "Deposits must be made from accounts registered in your name. We do not accept third-party deposits. The minimum deposit amount is $10 or the equivalent in your local currency.",
  },
  {
    title: "4. Withdrawal Process",
    content:
      "Withdrawals must be processed using the same method as the deposit. The minimum withdrawal amount is $10. Processing times vary depending on the payment provider.",
  },
  {
    title: "5. Processing Time",
    content:
      "Deposits are usually processed instantly, while withdrawals may take up to 3 business days. Delays may occur due to bank processing times or verification requirements.",
  },
  {
    title: "6. Fees and Charges",
    content:
      "VertexOption does not charge fees for deposits or withdrawals. However, your payment provider may impose transaction fees, which are your responsibility.",
  },
  {
    title: "7. Currency Exchange",
    content:
      "If your deposit or withdrawal is in a currency other than USD, conversion rates will apply based on the payment providerâ€™s exchange rates. We are not responsible for any rate fluctuations.",
  },
  {
    title: "8. Payment Verification",
    content:
      "For security reasons, we may require additional verification before processing transactions, including proof of identity or ownership of the payment method used.",
  },
  {
    title: "9. Refund Policy",
    content:
      "Refunds are only applicable in cases of incorrect transactions or duplicate payments. Refunds will be processed to the original payment source within 5-7 business days.",
  },
  {
    title: "10. Fraud Prevention",
    content:
      "To protect our users, VertexOption employs strict fraud prevention measures. Any suspicious activity may result in account suspension or additional verification requirements.",
  },
  {
    title: "11. Changes to Payment Policy",
    content:
      "We reserve the right to update this Payment Policy at any time. Continued use of our services after updates signifies your acceptance of the new policy.",
  },
  {
    title: "12. Contact Information",
    content:
      "If you have any questions regarding payments, please contact our support team at support@vertexoption.com.",
  },
];
---

<Layout>
  <section class="box mb-20 mt-10 px-6 py-12">
    <p class="text-4xl">Payment Policy</p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-10">
      {
        paymentPolicy.map(({ title, content }) => (
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold">{title}</p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-[#95A0B6]">{content}</p>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
